name: LOW PASS! AirSprint's FIRST Embraer Praetor 500 Arriving at Calgary Airport!
description:
On March 12th, 2021, AirSprint Private Aviation took delivery of their first Embraer Praetor 500 business jet at their headquarters in Calgary!

AirSprint already flies a fleet of Embraer Legacy 450s, but took the option to convert two examples to the Praetor 500 standard, which increases the aircraft's maximum range and also adds those stylish new winglets.

Congratulations to AirSprint, thanks for putting on a show for us!
